longBusinessSummary: 4imprint Group plc operates as a direct marketer of promotional products in North America, the United Kingdom, and Ireland. It offers apparel, bags, drinkware, and stationery, as well as writing, technology, outdoor and leisure, tradeshows and signage, auto, home and tools, and wellness and safety products. The company markets its products to individuals in businesses and organizations. 4imprint Group plc was incorporated in 1921 and is based in London, the United Kingdom.
